title: Super 16 - 16 bit music pack
description: 14 songs that will take you back to the good old days of the fourth generation of consoles!
longDescription:
FM and sample sounds of the fourth generation still echo like the sound of a distant thunder, but these 14 songs will take you right back into the eye of the storm!

14 tracks inspired by the sounds of two flagship consoles of the fourth generation, ranging from adventure to full on high octane action.

Listen to the tracks HERE
